{"word":"σανίδιον","slug":"σανίδιον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σανίδιον</b></el> <el>(σᾰνίδιον, ου, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Diminutive'>Dim.</a> of <a href='S:σανίς'><el>σανίς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a small trencher</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>like <el>πινάκιον</el>, <i>a tablet</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}